{"tid":2274901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥長青和牛店上月遭「淋紅油」 今宣佈退股劃清界線","createTime":"2020-11-06T17:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T21:05:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"67f43ceb7d86fa7245247228f52a503c69553f78","tid":2274901,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:50:35.000Z","msg":"前大台藝人麥長責（麥包）早前投資過百萬，與朋友在大坑開設和牛食材專門店，不過上月和牛店卻遭人淋紅油，當時麥包指不知道發生甚麼事，只表示已交由警方處理。事發未夠一個月，麥包老婆今日在社交網站中宣佈已退股，與和牛店劃清界線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201106/N5F5HEBFVBHFFGTBBEBLA6NZWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201106%2FN5F5HEBFVBHFFGTBBEBLA6NZWI%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9pKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=6f68dce8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201106%2FN5F5HEBFVBHFFGTBBEBLA6NZWI%2F&h=6e37b5f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201106/N5F5HEBFVBHFFGTBBEBLA6NZWI/</a>"},{"pid":"4faf20a30d837e39cd9aa5c4f59ae800c2a88424","tid":2274901,"uid":203431,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:52:16.000Z","msg":"整乜衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢究竟想點"},{"pid":"7ff605f0a4c91212527f64f1b52c30482ff3ca11","tid":2274901,"uid":301989,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"4faf20a30d837e39cd9aa5c4f59ae800c2a88424","tid":2274901,"uid":203431,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:52:16.000Z","msg":"整乜衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢究竟想點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"呢件真係垃撚圾嚟 廢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac